-- Skill Slot Repurposing Reference
-- This file is a reference document, NOT a functional script (.disabled so
-- it won't load). Catalogs how and why this project's "Misc" skill slots
-- (const.Skills 24-38) have been changed from their vanilla function, and
-- the three reusable patterns for doing this safely, established across a
-- single long session of iterating on Guardian/Cleave/ManaShield/Retaliation.
--
-- Note: "Guardian" was originally built and named "Cover" -- renamed after
-- a follow-up session folded a lightweight Taunt mechanic into it (see
-- Guardian.lua's own header). Older notes/commit messages referencing
-- "Cover" mean this same skill.
--
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
